title: [Catacombs, Pool]
description: Cobwebs have woven themselves over humanoid remains that have been carefully placed in the niches carved into stone walls.

Cobwebs have woven themselves over humanoid remains that have been carefully placed in the niches carved into stone walls.  Coarse dirt grinds against the rough cobbles underfoot, and the scratchy sound echoes off of the hard surfaces of the cavern.  Pools of murky water have collected in the low spots of the floor.
